initial_drafts.What sections are covered by this insura:
The Policy consists of: 
- this document which sets out the standard terms of Your cover and its limitations; 
- Your current Schedule issued by Us; 
- any other change to the terms of the Policy otherwise advised by Us in writing (such as an Endorsement or Supplementary PDS) before You enter into the Policy or where required or permitted by law. (pp. 9, 10)

Each Section may also contain definitions relevant to that Section of the Policy. (p. 11)

